    meta:
        description = "Evasion bypass rule"
        cape_options = "bp0=$pattern0+0,action0=skip,bp1=$pattern1+0,action1=skip,bp2=$pattern2+0,action2=skip,count=0"

    strings:
        $pattern0 = { 83 C4 14 52 FF D0 }  // add esp,14h | push edx | call eax
        $pattern1 = { 85 C0 77 B8 8B 45 ?? }  // test eax, eax | jnbe | mov eax,[ebp+??
        $pattern2 = { 52 E8 ?? ?? ?? ?? 52 }  // push edx | call | push edx

    condition:
        any of them
}
